  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13092623/masthead-gif-animation.gif" alt="Let's go skiing" data-udi="umb://media/034bc9bd9b044281b89eb31dda630185" /></p>
<p>You love it all - somewhere thrilling, with views that are breathtaking, to enjoy whilst chilling, spend days exploring and nights relaxing, you're there for the whole package. Discover our best hotels and resorts to give you a taste of it all.</p>
<h2>Accommodations</h2>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d}" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl"><strong>Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl, Obergurgl</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d}" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl"><img src="/media/13088456/hotel-edelweiss-gurgl-obergurgl.jpg" alt="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl - Obergurgl" data-udi="umb://media/182f0c8e64ff46c5a157adcfa0ffe20c" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Ski rental shop in the hotel.</li>
<li>Hotel leads straight outside to a choice of two lifts.</li>
<li>Highest altitude resort in <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> with great off-piste and amazing snow record.</li>
<li>Great family option, the resort has a very good ski school.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958}" title="Hotel Alpenblume"><strong>Hotel Alpenblume, Obergurgl</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d336aa6ddd24ea9b4b57ccaf8abb958}" title="Hotel Alpenblume"><img src="/media/13088514/hotel-alpenblume-obergurgl.jpg" alt="Hotel Alpenblume – Obergurgl" data-udi="umb://media/9c777fee5400457ba0f937504a2d6538" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Skiing in <a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl</a> is suited to all abilities - good for mixed groups.</li>
<li>Only two minutes’ walk from the nearest piste and ski school meeting point.</li>
<li>Great choice of room types, suites for families and great for groups too.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3}" title="Hotel Val Claret All Inclusive"><strong>Hotel Val Claret, Tignes</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9cd744ad4364e86a0ce2a71fc25c3c3}" title="Hotel Val Claret All Inclusive"><img src="/media/13088468/hotel-val-claret-inclusive-tignes.jpg" alt="Hotel Val Claret All Inclusive - Tignes" data-udi="umb://media/8330f4d379294987a8ac463597064e37" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Perfectly located in Val Claret just by the Bollin chairift.</li>
<li>Ski-in ski-out location.</li>
<li>All inclusive - breakfast, lunch, dinner and drinks included.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/f72f52b947094429a1a17a67b5ea9a51" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f72f52b947094429a1a17a67b5ea9a51}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isère Half Price Lift Pass Offer">Buy one get half price</a> on Lift Passes for the Tignes-Val d'Isére Ski Area. </li>
</ul>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a3dc19a519d54b058f439292419cb364" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a3dc19a519d54b058f439292419cb364}" title="Hotel Ambassador"><strong>Hotel Ambassador, Zermatt</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/a3dc19a519d54b058f439292419cb364" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a3dc19a519d54b058f439292419cb364}" title="Hotel Ambassador"><img src="/media/13088518/hotel-ambassador-zermatt.jpg" alt="Hotel Ambassador – Zermatt" data-udi="umb://media/53f9bc21c6b74de39c5f4b26b032b4b6" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Relaxed and spacious hotel with good facilities including bar, lounge, restaurant and spa.</li>
<li>Variety of modern and stylish rooms and suites on offer.</li>
<li>Located at the foot of <a data-udi="umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4abc3d9367fc4903a52b296414b05ef1}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt’s</a> main street - close to ski school and lifts.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba"><strong>Sporthotel Arabba, Arabba</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba"><img src="/media/13088463/sport-hotel-arabba.jpg" alt="Sport Hotel Arabba - Arabba" data-udi="umb://media/fc0a92ee318349fcb1f21ce5e1398816" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>100m to nearest lift, plus great links to the rest of the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites.</a></li>
<li>The resort is near the Marmolada glacier, so expect challenging reds and black runs.</li>
<li>You can arrange heli-skiing on the glacier. </li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p style="color: #003155;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil"><strong>Hotel Cimes du Soleil, Avoriaz</strong></a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil"><img src="/media/13088522/hotel-les-cimes-du-soleil-avoriaz.jpg" alt="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil – Avoriaz" data-udi="umb://media/fb65359838f54173963f1141b80a2a44" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Ski-in ski-out</li>
<li>Hotel is informal with lots of interconnecting rooms - to keep your group close together.</li>
<li>Bar, lounge, restaurants and games room to keep everyone entertained.</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div></div>
<div> </div>
