<h2>Ski Resorts</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes/Val d'Isere Ski Area - France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13092746/valdisere-408x200.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1e95ac6c2e904f20a0deef1476cb9b8e" /><img style="width: 408px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13092746/valdisere-408x200.jpg?width=408&amp;height=200" alt="Tignes/Val d'Isere Ski Area - France" data-udi="umb://media/1e95ac6c2e904f20a0deef1476cb9b8e" /><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13092746/valdisere-408x200.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="Tignes/Val d'Isere Ski Area - France" data-udi="umb://media/1e95ac6c2e904f20a0deef1476cb9b8e" /><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13092746/valdisere-408x200.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="Val d'Isere Ski Area" data-udi="umb://media/1e95ac6c2e904f20a0deef1476cb9b8e" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are seeking the thrill of the snow but the culture of an alpine village, then this is the ideal location. Linking the two famous resorts in France, these skiing </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and snowboarding </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">areas have options for all types of ability. The iconic area offers lots of cafes, shops and a lively nightlife. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578" href="/{localLink:umb://document/72a5198213b1400d8c891f49fe57b578}" title="Three Valleys Ski Area">The Three Valleys Ski Area - France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 408px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13092760/threevalleys-408x200.jpg?width=408&amp;height=200" alt="Three Valleys Ski Area - France" data-udi="umb://media/bb51259336894747aacb6e21849dd110" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pistes with a challenge, including moguls and chutes – these linked French resorts mean this area offers endless runs. The potential for ski </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and snowboarding</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> adventure is infinite, with plenty of lifts to get you there. This diverse area provides a lifestyle holiday experience from culture rich cooking classes to local live music nights.  </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c24998bb7c5140ed8ec0febaf0a46fa2}" title="Arlberg Ski Area">Arlberg Ski Area - Austria</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13092748/austria-408x200.jpg" alt="Austria Ski resorts" data-udi="umb://media/53237596392e409794f5da13450910f0" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are looking for a full winter adventure, western Austria offers you this. Ski </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and snowboard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a variety of slopes, all with easy access and multiple cable car options. Finding further excitement with the resort's abundant activities from tobogganing, sleigh-rides to curling. </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites Ski Area - Italy</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13092758/thedolomites-408x200.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="Dolomites Ski area - Italy" data-udi="umb://media/3bf740e50cd24f3895657506b74e14c4" /><img style="width: 408px; height: 200px;" src="/media/13092759/thedolomites-408x200.jpg?width=408&amp;height=200" alt="Dolomites Ski Area - Italy" data-udi="umb://media/b0a09b42790d4d37862b5fcfb047e741" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Where better to navigate Italy’s genuinely beautiful slopes than within the most photogenic mountain peaks. By day, ski </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">and snowboard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> with ease via the many lifts and by night, delight in the local Italian cuisine. If you want to appreciate all this area has to offer, opt for some adventurous Paragliding or a trip into the Hidden Valley.  </span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Looking for more inspiration?</h2>
<p>Why not find out more about all our ski holidays as we love them all! We have compiled a series of <a data-udi="umb://document/08f2c95a400f49b187febb5058955b5b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/08f2c95a400f49b187febb5058955b5b}" title="Winter Insider Guides">Insider’s Guides</a>, from our in-house insider knowledge to bring you the best the mountains have to offer.</p>
